RIYADH: French football club Paris Saint-Germain (PSG), including stars Lionel Messi, Neymar, Kylian Mbappe, Achraf Hakimi and Marquinhos, will face off against the stars of Al-Hilal and Al-Nassr for the Riyadh Season Cup. For the latest updates, follow us on Twitter @ArabNewsSport The match will be played in Riyadh on January 19 at King Fahd International Stadium, and the players of Al-Hilal and Al-Nassr will turn from traditional rivals into a unified team under the leadership of an international coach and assistant. The winning team will receive Riyadh Season 2022 Cup. The match will be broadcast live on PSG.fr, PSG social media and the beIN sports network. The match will be accompanied by entertaining activities, light shows and fireworks, as part of the Riyadh Season festivities. 